text: Ebou Kanteh (born 12 February 1995) is a Gambian international footballer who plays as a midfielder. ==Career== Born in Brikama, he has played club football for Brikama United and Real de Banjul. He spent time in 2019 with Sheikh Jamal Dhanmondi Club.
